{"title":"Chris King Gets Tropical with the Re-Release of Matte Mango","link":"https://bikerumor.com/chris-king-gets-tropical-with-the-re-release-of-matte-mango/","date":1699373088000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-the-gang.jpeg\" alt=\"Chris King Components Matte Mango the gang\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-the-gang.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-the-gang-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-the-gang-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-the-gang-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-the-gang-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-the-gang-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Portland, Oregon’s <a href=\"https://chrisking.com/\">alchemy masters of color</a>, Chris King Precision Components is at it again. Their new re-release color is bursting through the dreary, grey skies of the PNW like it’s from a tropical island paradise. That’s right kids, after an 18-month-long vacation, the <a href=\"https://chrisking.com/blogs/news/matte-mango\">popular and tropical color</a>, Matte Mango is back. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-words.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-words.jpeg\" alt=\"Chris King Components Matte Mango words\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-words.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-words-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-words-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-words-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-words-768x768.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo/Chris King Precision Components</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Matte Mango will be a part of CK’s 2024 color assortment from now on. That means it’ll be a permanent fixture in the blingy line with the rest of the crowd, like Black, Matte Black, Two Tone Black Gold, Midnight, Matte Turquoise, Red, Silver, Gold, and 3D Violet.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-bottom-bracket-e1699371376409.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"552\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-bottom-bracket-e1699371376409.jpeg\" alt=\"Chris King Components Matte Mango bottom bracket\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-bottom-bracket-e1699371376409.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-bottom-bracket-e1699371376409-297x128.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-bottom-bracket-e1699371376409-800x345.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-bottom-bracket-e1699371376409-120x52.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-bottom-bracket-e1699371376409-768x331.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub.jpeg\" alt=\"Chris King Components Matte Mango rear hub\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub-768x768.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-grouped-.jpeg\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-grouped-.jpeg\" alt=\"Chris King Components Matte Mango grouped\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-grouped-.jpeg 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-grouped--240x300.jpeg 240w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-grouped--800x1000.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-grouped--96x120.jpeg 96w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-grouped--768x960.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If you remember, Chris King was one of the first component companies to offer color anodization, back in 1988. They are adding and removing colors to and from the collection, like <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/chris-king-3d-violet-purple-hubs-headset/\">adding 3D Violet</a> back to the line that first appeared in ’88. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-headset-and-stack.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-headset-and-stack.jpeg\" alt=\"Chris King Components Matte Mango headset and stack\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-headset-and-stack.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-headset-and-stack-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-headset-and-stack-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-headset-and-stack-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-headset-and-stack-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-headset-and-stack-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-headset.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-headset.jpeg\" alt=\"Chris King Components Matte Mango headset\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-headset.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-headset-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-headset-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-headset-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-headset-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-headset-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>“Consistent, high-quality anodizing isn’t easy. Without constant monitoring and attention to detail, anodizing can vary from batch to batch, and from material to material. We take great care to ensure that every customer gets a headset, bottom bracket, and hubs that closely match</em>,” states King Sales Manager, Greg Hudson. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub.jpeg\" alt=\"Chris King Components Matte Mango rear hub\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub-768x768.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub-in-bike.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub-in-bike.jpeg\" alt=\"Chris King Components Matte Mango rear hub in bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub-in-bike.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub-in-bike-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub-in-bike-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub-in-bike-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub-in-bike-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-rear-hub-in-bike-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-front-hub.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-front-hub.jpeg\" alt=\"Chris King Components Matte Mango front hub\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-front-hub.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-front-hub-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-front-hub-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-front-hub-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-front-hub-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-front-hub-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Hudson continues, “<em>In 2022, we were struggling to consistently get our Matte Mango within tolerance, which caused production delays and increased our lead-times. Instead of shipping mismatched components to discerning customers who expect the very best, we removed Matte Mango from the assortment. Now, we’re excited to welcome one of our favorite colors back</em>!” </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-front-hub-match-with-fork-e1699371327493.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Chris-King-Components-Matte-Mango-front-hub-match-with-fork.jpeg\" alt=\"Chris King Components Matte Mango front hub match with fork\" /></a><figcaption>Matchy, matchy.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Matte Mango as well as the other amazing colors are available now! Just hit the link below to introduce a lil’ paradise to your ride.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://chrisking.com/\">ChrisKing.com </a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/chris-king-gets-tropical-with-the-re-release-of-matte-mango/\">Chris King Gets Tropical with the Re-Release of Matte Mango</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"3e463637f65482f3d2053b789f7f94ef68bee29b20c2aa56a749f68f660673ce","category":"Cycling"}